results.deck: SCE Cambridge is a game development company and publisher most famous for the Medievil franchise and work on LittleBigPlanet. They are based in Cambridge, England.
results.description:
Overview

Guerrilla Cambridge, formerly SCE Studio Cambridge and Millenium Interactive before that, gained some fame for publishing the James Pond series of platformers. After an acquisition through Sony in 1997, the company was renamed into SCE Cambridge where they developed the MediEvil franchise as well as Primal and 24: The Game on PlayStation 2. The studio is currently working on the 5th installment of the Killzone franchise named Killzone: Mercernary which is being developed for the PlayStation Vita.
